#- 11/30/13
Apartment Room 5A, South Aurora. Broke window to get in, broke open a chest. Got a diamond pickaxe.

Churchill Store. Broke open two chests. Took flint and steel, 3 3/4 stacks of lapis.

Westside. Burned
#- Gravelstone Apartments building and a neighboring building down.

Burned down the Institute. Stole nothing, broke into several chests.

Broke into Krank2015's Modern House.
#- Burned down Sofaball64's House. Benburt saw me do it.
